title: CORRECTED-MOVES-Temasek names Lee Theng Kiat CEO of Temasek International
text:
Published By: Reuters - Company News - Today 
Sept 30 (Reuters) - Temasek Holdings Ltd appointed Lee Theng Kiat as chief executive of Temasek International effective Oct. 1....
